{
  "thoughts": "I need to add a new 'Live Data' item to the app's sidebar and ensure it navigates to a new, empty screen. I'll first explore the project structure to find the renderer navigation and sidebar components, then create a new screen component and add a route and sidebar link. I will also update docs/FILE_ORGANISATION.md only if new major directories are added (likely not needed).",
  "tool_calls": [
    {
      "tool_name": "list_files",
      "arguments": {
        "path": "."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "thoughts": "Next, inspect the src directory to locate renderer components, sidebar, and routing setup, so I can add a new Live Data screen and navigation item.",
  "tool_calls": [
    {
      "tool_name": "list_files",
      "arguments": {
        "path": "src"
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "thoughts": "Dive into src/renderer to find the UI components, sidebar, and router configuration. Then add a new screen component and add a route and a sidebar item for 'Live Data'.",
  "tool_calls": [
    {
      "tool_name": "list_files",
      "arguments": {
        "path": "src/renderer"
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "thoughts": "Open renderer/navigation to find routing and sidebar implementation files, then inspect components that might contain the sidebar. After understanding structure, create a new screen under screens (e.g., LiveDataScreen.tsx), register a route in navigation, and add a sidebar item linking to that route.",
  "tool_calls": [
    {
      "tool_name": "list_files",
      "arguments": {
        "path": "src/renderer/navigation"
      }
    },
    {
      "tool_name": "list_files",
      "arguments": {
        "path": "src/renderer/components"
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "thoughts": "I will inspect the existing navigation and screens to understand how routes and sidebar items are defined, then add a new Live Data screen and corresponding sidebar navigation entry.",
  "tool_calls": [
    {
      "tool_name": "read_files",
      "arguments": {
        "paths": [
          "src/renderer/navigation/Navigator.tsx",
          "src/renderer/navigation/SidebarView.tsx",
          "src/renderer/navigation/filesNavigation.ts",
          "src/renderer/screens"
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "thoughts": "I should inspect types to add a new NavigationView option for 'Live Data', then update Navigator to parse and navigate to it, create a new screen component, and add a new sidebar item with an icon that navigates to this view.",
  "tool_calls": [
    {
      "tool_name": "read_files",
      "arguments": {
        "paths": [
          "src/renderer/types.ts"
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
